channel.title: FroyoScape is in need of a Web Developer!
channel.description:
FroyoScape is looking for a web developer, which in another point of view can be viewed as the painter. They paint the 'building', and this building you can call the server. Who's looking to be a painter, for FroyoScape?
[ol][li]Start by filling in [iurl=#application]the application[/iurl].[/li] [li]After that, you will be in pending, so if I do not reply right away, that means you are pending.[/li] [li]If you are accepted, then welcome to out skype group chat! In there, you will meet staff members Flame_, ox random xi, amy_webb, and AtomicInt_. And of course me. Feel free to ask us ANYTHING.[/li][/ol]
[size=18pt]While you are pending...[/size]
[ul][li]you may be PMed by me or any other staff member questions.[/li] [li]you will be pending for about 1 - 3 days.[/li][/ul]
[size=18pt]If you would like to contact me or any other person on the team...[/size]
[ul][li]ask me on skype (Skype: thunderstrike420). If you'd like to talk to another person, I will redirect you to them.[/li][/ul]
[anchor=application]Here's the application! [code=application] Name: Age: Previous work: Skype: [/code]
